ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I thoroughly enjoyed the class, and would highly recommend it. It was a very good class to be in, especially because it introduces students to how certain experiments and techniques are used.
taking Chem Bio I first was very helpful!

Yes, I would definitely recommend this class, as it helps a student develop a variety of skills, e.g. how to efficiently analyze a paper, how to prepare a discussion section/presentation, or how to come up with exam questions about a certain topic covered in class.
